OL,3,CHorizon scandal: Post Office should
OL,4,Cpay for therapy, say sub-postmasters
OL,6,FSub-postmasters and their families are
OL,7,Fstill dealing with the long-term
OL,8,Fpsychological impact of wrongful
OL,9,Faccusations and convictions, with
OL,10,Fdelays to justice 'retraumatising'
OL,11,Fvictims of the Post Office Horizon IT
OL,12,Fscandal, a new study finds
OL,14,FWrongly accused and wrongly convicted
OL,15,FSubpostmasters have said the Post
OL,16,FOffice should pay for therapy and
OL,17,Fcounselling "for life" due to the
OL,18,Fongoing trauma caused by the Horizon
OL,19,FIT Scandal.
