OL,3,CHorizon scandal: Post Office should
OL,4,Cpay for therapy, say sub-postmasters
OL,6,FVictims and their families say those
OL,7,Fwho need mental health support should
OL,8,Fnot have to wait for compensation or
OL,9,Fuse their own money to pay for help.
OL,11,FA new study, 'Understanding the
OL,12,FImpacts of the Post Office Scandal',
OL,13,Fgiven exclusively to ITV News, has
OL,14,Fdocumented for the first time the
OL,15,Fongoing psychological and emotional
OL,16,Fdamage inflicted to the men and women
OL,17,Fwho were interrogated and incarcerated
OL,18,Fdue to errors in the Post Office's IT
OL,19,Fsystem run by Fujitsu.
