OL,6,FThe report is part of the 'Post Office
OL,7,FProject,' which has interviewed dozens
OL,8,Fof subpostmasters and their families,
OL,9,Fand aims to explore the ethical and
OL,10,Flegal lessons from the Horizon Scandal
OL,11,Fto improve the criminal justice system.
OL,13,FParmod Kalia ran a Post Office Branch
OL,14,Fin Orpington in Kent for over a decade
OL,15,Fwhen he was wrongly accused of theft
OL,16,Fin 2001. The father of four was
OL,17,Fsentenced to six months in prison and
OL,18,Fforced to pay #22,000 to the Post
OL,19,FOffice despite there being no proof he
OL,20,Fstole it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
