OL,3,CHorizon scandal: Post Office should
OL,4,Cpay for therapy, say sub-postmasters
OL,6,FHe says the conviction destroyed his
OL,7,Flife and nearly cost him his marriage.
OL,8,FHe told ITV News he sought therapy
OL,9,Fafter attempting to take his own life.
OL,11,F"It was horrendous, it was horrible...
OL,12,F25 years of my life has been ruined by
OL,13,Fthe Post Office," Parmod says.
OL,15,F"My children did actually ask me at
OL,16,Fthe time, 'Dad, have you taken the
OL,17,Fmoney?'. They were six and nine years
OL,18,Fold at the time."
