OL,6,FProfessor Richard Moorhead, lead
OL,7,Fauthor of the report, said, "The thing
OL,8,Fthat stands out from this work is the
OL,9,Fway an unjust accusation by the Post
OL,10,FOffice has spread through the lives of
OL,11,Fthose accused and their families."
OL,13,F"With the exception of the ongoing
OL,14,FInquiry, formal responses have tended
OL,15,Fto be cold and adversarial, which has
OL,16,Fbeen harmful to victims."
