OL,6,F"It's not just the sub-postmasters who
OL,7,Fhave been (impacted) by this. It goes
OL,8,Fright across the families. It's
OL,9,Fhorrendous."
OL,11,F"But the government refuse to accept
OL,12,Fthat... they will not take on board
OL,13,Fthe damage that's been inflicted on
OL,14,Ffamilies as part of any settlement or
OL,15,Fin a review of cases. It's clearly
OL,16,Fbased on the sub-postmasters'
OL,17,Fearnings. But many of these businesses
OL,18,Fwere family-run," he said.
